title: Buried Alive
itunes:title: Buried Alive
description:
Do you have dreams in your life that you have buried, so to speak? Maybe your dream was to be free from addiction, to have a healthy marriage, or to fulfill your God-given purpose, but you thought it was impossible so you stopped believing. The good news is that God is a God who brings dead things back to life. Be encouraged through this message to begin believing for your dreams again!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
